channel.title: Project Insanity
channel.description: I'm newish to coding and I have never coded a PI server before. Can anyone point me into the right direction to code my server?

item.title: Project Insanity
item.dc:creator: @imstrength imstrength
item.description:
@imstrength wrote:

f*ck all that. when i started all i did was download my favorite servers source and start with no idea what i was doing. play around with it a bit. make sure you do a backup before everything you add incase you completely fail you have a copy to go back to. the more back ups the better.

and also if you ever need help with something that you reaaally cant figure out yourself then post here. i suggest though that you try to ask as little questions on here as possible. try to learn it yourself and google EVERYTHING before posting here. if all it takes is a simple google search to answer a question people wont like you very much around here haha

but goodluck for sure whatever you decide to do man!
